com.gwtplatform.dispatch.client.gin

Class AbstractDispatchAsyncModule.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.client.gin.AbstractDispatchAsyncModule.Builder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DispatchAsyncModule.Builder, RestDispatchAsyncModuleBuilder, RpcDispatchAsyncModule.Builder
    Enclosing class:
    AbstractDispatchAsyncModule

    public abstract static class AbstractDispatchAsyncModule.Builder
extends Object
    A AbstractDispatchAsyncModule builder.

    By default, this builder configures the AbstractDispatchAsyncModule to use DefaultExceptionHandler, DefaultClientActionHandlerRegistry and DefaultSecurityCookieAccessor.

    See Also:
    RpcDispatchAsyncModule.Builder, RestDispatchAsyncModule.Builder
